snippet.title: Whisker Squadron Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Support the project here:
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/flippfly/whisker-squadron?ref=e4de8e

From the creators of Race The Sun. Flippfly's take on forward-scrolling aerial combat. Fight your way through a procedurally-generated mission with your choice of feline heroes. Coming to PC and consoles in 2022

Music by Chel Wong
